headline: With Competition Rising, Should Investors Give Up On This Top Growth Stock?
summary: Intuitive Surgical has had little competition for its famous da Vinci system in the U.S.  Intuitive Surgical (NASDAQ: ISRG) has delivered market-crushing returns over the past two decades, thanks to its leadership in the robotic-assisted surgery (RAS) market.  Part of the company's appeal is that its crown jewel has had little competition.
